preambule.al:
Whereas the Republic of Finland
wishes to assist the Kingdom of the Netherlands, in respect of Aruba,
in diversifying its economy;

li.al:
in the case of Aruba, the Minister of Finance
and Economic Affairs or an authorised representative of the
Minister;

preambule.al:
Aangezien de Republiek Finland het Koninkrijk
